    "title": "Kusudi la Hukumu",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "kusudi la hukumu",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Kusudi la hukumu za Mungu ni lipi? Je, zinalenga kuleta ukombozi, au ni kwa ajili ya uharibifu pekee? Hukumu katika kitabu cha Ufunuo zinatoa vidokezo fulani.</p><p>Mwisho wa tarumbeta ya sita, licha ya mapigo yote, watu &quot;bado hawakutubu matendo ya mikono yao&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev9:20-Rev9:21\">Ufunuo 9:20–21</a>). Baadhi ya watu hawatabadilika, haijalishi nini kinawatokea, hata chini ya shinikizo.</p><p>Watu walioteswa na tarumbeta ya tano walitamani kufa badala ya kumgeukia Mungu kwa toba (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev9:6\">9:6</a>). Wengi huchagua kifo badala ya kukiri dhambi zao.</p><p>Katika muhuri wa sita, watu waliomba miamba iwaangukie ili iwafiche kutokana na &quot;ghadhabu ya Mwanakondoo&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:12-Rev6:17\">6:12–17</a>). Tamaa yao ya kuepuka hukumu inaonyesha hofu badala ya imani kwa Mungu.</p><p>Ufunuo unasisitiza haki ya mwisho ya Mungu na dhana ya malipo au kulipiza kisasi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:5-Rev16:7\">16:5–7</a>). Wote Wakristo na wasio Wakristo watapata wanachostahili (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:23\">2:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev11:18\">11:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:13\">14:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:6\">18:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:12-Rev20:13\">20:12–13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:12\">22:12</a>).</p><p>Hukumu ni majibu ya Mungu kwa maombi ya watakatifu kwa ajili ya haki. Hukumu hutokea kwa wakati wa Mungu, si wetu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:9-Rev6:11\">6:9–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev8:2-Rev8:5\">8:2–5</a>).</p><p>Hukumu, kama ilivyokuwa kwa mapigo ya Misri, zinaonyesha kwamba miungu ya duniani na maadui wa Mungu hawana nguvu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:8-Exod7:12\">Kutoka 7:8–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:12\">12:12</a>; linganisha <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev13:4-Rev13:17\">Ufunuo 13:4–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:20-Rev19:21\">19:20–21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:9-Rev20:10\">20:9–10</a>).</p><p>Hukumu ni sehemu ya misheni ya Mungu na zinatoa fursa ya mwisho ya kutubu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:6-Rev14:7\">Ufunuo 14:6–7</a>; tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev9:20-Rev9:21\">9:20–21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:9\">16:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:11\">11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:21\">21</a>).</p><p>Mungu ameweka wazi kwamba dhambi ni mbaya na hukumu inakuja (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:5-Rom2:11\">Warumi 2:5–11</a>). Hata hivyo, watu wengi bado wanakataa kutubu na kukubali neema ya Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:32\">Warumi 1:32</a>). Hata katika siku za mwisho, wakati Mungu anapotuma mashahidi wake kuonya juu ya maangamizi yanayokuja, wengi watachagua kuunga mkono nguvu za uovu. Watafurahia kuanguka kwa manabii wa Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev11:3-Rev11:10\">Ufunuo 11:3–10</a>). Wale wanaompinga Mungu na kumgeuka, hatimaye atawaondoa kutoka katika uwepo wake.</p><p>Hukumu kwa kutotii na matendo maovu ni hakika (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:18-Rom2:11\">Warumi 1:18–2:11</a>). Hata hivyo, Mungu kwa uvumilivu anasubiri watu watubu na anatoa neema yake (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:4\">Warumi 2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:8-2Pet3:10\">2 Petro 3:8–10</a>). Kwa hivyo, maonyo haya kuhusu hukumu yanaweza kuwa fursa ya mabadiliko.</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kusoma Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod6:6\">Kutoka 6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:12\">12:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:25\">Mambo ya Walawi 26:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:7-2Kgs17:23\">2 Wafalme 17:7–23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:6\">Zaburi 103:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:11\">Mithali 16:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:11\">Isaya 13:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:21\">26:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:18\">59:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:1-Jer5:9\">Yeremia 5:1–9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek11:21\">Ezekieli 11:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek39:21-Ezek39:24\">39:21–24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph1:12\">Sefania 1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:5\">Malaki 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:47\">Luka 12:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:30\">Yohana 5:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:2-Rom2:11\">Warumi 2:2–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:1-Heb2:4\">Waebrania 2:1–4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:29\">10:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev9:20-Rev9:21\">Ufunuo 9:20–21</a></p>",
